descript.abstract:
Holdridge lifezones of Puerto Rico and the US Virgin Islands.
Puerto Rico data obtained from the lifezones.e00 export file of IITF. Coastlines of Vieques, Culebra, and Isla Mona obtained from the pvcm_coast.e00 export file of IITF. Inner polygons of Vieques obtained by scanning original Ewell and Whitmore map (1973, scale 1:250,000), georeferencing the image using Erdas Imagine and then "heads-up" digitizing. USVI lifezones digitized onscreen from scanned original Ewell and Whitmore Life Zones map.
